      <title>马克龙高风险投票试图阻止勒庞进军法国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/european-elections-2024-macron-calls-vote-in-effort-to-halt-advance-of-le-pen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在周日的欧洲议会选举中惨败后，法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙呼吁提前举行立法选举，以阻止其极右翼对手玛丽娜·勒庞的崛起。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/european-elections-2024-macron-calls-vote-in-effort-to-halt-advance-of-le-pen</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 23:26:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
